title: Teclast debuts new affordable tablet with large display and up to 1 TB expandable storage
description: The Teclast T65 2026 is another affordable tablet from the company. Powered by the Unisoc T7280, the tab features a 13.4-inch IPS display with a 120 Hz refresh rate and has support for up to 1 TB of expandable storage. It has a retail price of $189.99.
content: Teclast has introduced a couple of new tabs, and there's another addition, the T65 2025. It's an affordable tablet that's powered by the Unisoc T7280, an entry-level eight-core CPU with the Mali G57 … [+1212 chars]
